  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 2
  Paragraph: 32
Title: Discussion On Making All Things Equal
---
So it is that long ago Yao said to Shun, "I want to attack the rulers
of Tsung, K'uai, and Hsu-ao. Even as I sit on my throne, this thought
nags at me. Why is this?"
